            <label>Justice Thurgood Marshall</label>
            <text syncTime="0.000" offset="0">The other case of Berkovitz is here on certiorari to the Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit.</text>
            <text syncTime="7.648" offset="30511">In that case, we hold that the discretionary function exception of the Federal Tort Claims Act does not bar petitioner's suit.</text>
            <text syncTime="18.054" offset="72202">Accordingly, we reverse the judgment of the Third Circuit.</text>
